<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/html" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/html">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/application.css"/>
<body class="email-body">

<h1>Welcome</h1>
<p class="center"><b><%=  @user.company.name %></b> added you to Elephant!</p>

<hr>

<br>
<p>Elephant will help make your job easier in many ways as you will soon come to find out. For starters, remember that it will be the first and primary spot to find documents, data, and communication for every job.</p>
<p><%= link_to "www.elephant-cloud.com", "www.elephant-cloud.com", class: "activity-user-link" %></p>

<hr>

<p>Login using your email: <%= @user.email %></p>
<p><b>This link below contains your temporary password:</b></p>
<p>
  <%= link_to "Click Here to Login Now", "www.elephant-cloud.com/update_password?new_account=true&email=" + @user.email + "&current_password=" + @password, class: "bluebtn" %>
</p>

<br><br>
<p>If the link above doesn't work, your temporary password is: <span class=""><%= @password %></span></p>

<% if Rails.env.production? %>
    <hr>
    <div class="center"><%= image_tag "blue_logo_small.png" %></div>
    <br>
<% end %>
</body>
</html>